  "text": "We found an increase in partner-reported behavioral symptoms, specifically anxiety and apathy, in those who progressed, and a non-significant increase in self-reported depression. These findings are supportive of earlier studies showing an increase in behavioral symptoms in subjects who develop MCI [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The difference in self-versus partner report of depression, anxiety and apathy warrants further investigation.",
